You suggested me this one immediately after publishing the song. I was playing card in the mean time. So couldn't listen immediately. Later on when I listened, I remembered your existence those days. We could have listen this one on watch together option. 
ma'am, you left some memories for me which are so special and alluring. I will remember those during my last days. I wish if I could back to those days once again. I literally mean it!
